Data manipulation

firesting2 <- firesting |>
  select(c(1:3,5:9)) |> 
  rename(TIME = `Time (HH:MM:SS)`, 
         dTIME = `Time (s)`, 
         ch1 = Ch1...5, 
         ch2 = Ch2...6,
         ch3 = Ch3...7, 
         ch4 = Ch4...8, 
         temperature= `Ch 1...9`) |> 
  select(c("dTIME",all_of(chamber),"TIME","temperature"))
